timestamp": 1612189353, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031855, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "世另我！！！", "timestamp": 1612189354, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031860, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: patpatDave", "timestamp": 1612189394, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031863, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: patpatFrancis", "timestamp": 1612189414, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031869, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢Carol和Eve君:）", "timestamp": 1612189471, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不过我最近拒绝的似乎会多一点点。感觉只是心理负担大一点", "timestamp": 1612189472, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031885, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 付出大于所得是人之常情吗，感觉有些认识的人即使自身不是特别热心，但还是很容易寻求到他人的帮助，好羡慕他们QAQ", "timestamp": 1612189598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我也是一拒绝就心理负担很重 orz", "timestamp": 1612189646, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031904, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那是你拒绝的还不够多。有高中同学提了我不能实现的要求我只能拒绝之后，我就发现拒绝，也没什么……", "timestamp": 1612189757, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031931, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 接受它就好了。其实真的没什么。(我最近就用这来接受拒绝的)", "timestamp": 1612190065, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1031966, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 204660, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好的！谢谢F君C君", "timestamp": 1612190465, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 204660, "reply": 19, "tag": null, "text": "感觉我真的好不擅长人际交往啊。不擅长拒绝别人的请求，而且帮别人忙之后别人一旦想做出什么表示感谢的举动也会出于礼貌拒绝，总觉得人家只是和我客套客套而已……所以在人际交往永远是付出大于所得。想改变这样的情况，该怎么做呢(ಥ_ಥ)", "timestamp": 1612189050, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1612190465, "url": "", "vote": {}}}